snippet.title: KEG WARS :: Trailer [HD]
snippet.description:
Keg Wars is a innovative tactical take on the classic TicTacToe game. In Keg Wars instead of crosses or circles, players chose cards with different abilities to dominate the game board and achieve a three-in-a-row winning scenario. Bronze Award Winner in Comic Con 2018. 
Powered by GameNest® and PlayStation® First.
